405172,"uid":129363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T16:07:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我一星期去1-2次，每次買4-500到。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買d咩,送禮自吃<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?<br />\n平時吃咩黑美人西瓜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自用，主要2個人食，有時拎D比屋企人。"},{"pid":"9bffca8802c5a5c9285bf615080160381faa7ea9","tid":405172,"uid":14423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T16:16:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主試吓買個日本桃食，食完唔想食平時果啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  可以分享食評?</blockquote><br />\n好甜，啲汁湧出黎<br />\n一生一定要試一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47c84e4d2b59c6bc67779d470ef4627d263e9809","tid":405172,"uid":35644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T16:22:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>樓主試吓買個日本桃食，食完唔想食平時果啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  可以分享食評?</blockquote><br />\n好甜，啲汁湧出黎<br />\n一生一定要試一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上次去日本食 係幾甜 但核個個位好苦 係咪正常?"},{"pid":"c766e6f9a7c75319369b75ffbca6b5048a2f3ee1","tid":405172,"uid":129363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T16:27:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>樓主試吓買個日本桃食，食完唔想食平時果啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" clas