人西瓜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之前個幾個月買夕張蜜瓜，每次買一個，加D蘋果，金奇異果，或其他。呢個幾月就買桃多，今年試咁多隻，係大唐嶺比較好。但整體都冇上年咁好。</blockquote><br />\n係咪吃過就唔會再吃街市同超市d水果<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},{"pid":"2096e8dc4b0c38f528c0a52119f0d5506f4cc5c9","tid":405172,"uid":139913,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T17:29:00.000Z","msg":"樓主窮撚<br />\n完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：星期日成日渣車落去買桃"},{"pid":"53dfc3dd2a78d454f5bf5587acb9b0dbcb1d9091","tid":405172,"uid":139913,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T17:29:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主窮撚<br />\n完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：星期日成日<span style=\"color: red;\">揸</span>車落去買桃</blockquote>"},{"pid":"73aeec7ab1e19f5ac967024a775af6385f5601e2","tid":405172,"uid":48917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T17:33:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主窮撚<br />\n完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：星期日成日渣車落去買桃</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買唔起貴生果 <br />\n好失敗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63a71b7f332880c53981de2ec9cbb6656fbe7936","tid":405172,"uid":139913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T17:36:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主窮撚<br />\n完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：星期日成日渣車落去買桃</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買唔起貴生果 <br />\n好失敗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係去買桃多<br />\n上星期買左蘋果 又大又甜又爽 <br />\ncp值幾高<br />\n樓豬唔買都可以行返轉食下生果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1b88ecd6d41d36c6386bd1da28ae3962db48513","tid":405172,"uid":105501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T17:39:18.000Z","msg":"前幾日同啊媽去完<br />\n佢會睇下相對上邊啲平啲又好食啲（有得試食）<br />\n我睇嗰間3個桃100蚊"},{"pid":"924388795f4937bc0a02e61635295518f8c319d1","tid":405172,"uid":48917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T17:39:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>樓主窮撚<br />\n完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：星期日成日渣車落去買桃</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買唔起貴生果 <br />\n好失敗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係去買桃多<br />\n上星期買左蘋果 又大又甜又爽 <br />\ncp值幾高<br />\n樓豬唔買都可以行返轉食下生果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n幾錢粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買有冇得試食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb3ec62a14521654d292dcae45a62307fc67e917","tid":405172,"uid":136309,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T17:40:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote> <br />\n<br />\n佢地對象 係商店定散客<br />\nd水果見到都覺得好貴 雖然話係日本貨姐<br />\n利申窮撚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n果欄本身係做批發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />凌晨先最旺，啲人一板板咁買平生果，日頭賣散客嗰啲係想做多round賺返啲碎銀啫，得幾丁友買咁對佢地嚟講梗係賣貴野先有賺啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：屋企前兩代都做開生果檔，同埋唔會去果欄買零售嘢"},{"pid":"f22094d03e3f261c1c09b779044a8393194bc2e4","tid":405172,"uid":139913,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T17:44:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>樓主窮撚<br />\n完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：星期日成日渣車落去買桃</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買唔起貴生果 <br />\n好失敗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係去買桃多<br />\n上星期買左蘋果 又大又甜又爽 <br />\ncp值幾高<br />\n樓豬唔買都可以行返轉食下生果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n幾錢粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買有冇得試食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係唔記得 多數帶五百蚊去<br />\n買完就算<br />\n其實當你去日本買生果返黎做手信價錢差唔多<br />\n利申：每次去日本/韓國都會買好多生果返香港<br />\n買唔買都有得試食<br />\n<br />\n我多數星期日 1700-1800去買<br />\n會再平多少少 因為佢地趕收工清貨"},{"pid":"bdb8bff26e1ecbcbaef9a874a69c4ad00f6ca0c4","tid":405172,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T17:45:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我一星期去1-2次，每次買4-500到。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買d咩,送禮自吃<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?<br />\n平時吃咩黑美人西瓜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之前個幾個月買夕張蜜瓜，每次買一個，加D蘋果，金奇異果，或其他。呢個幾月就買桃多，今年試咁多隻，係大唐嶺比較好。但整體都冇上年咁好。</blockquote><br />\n啲香印提字都唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過宮崎芒果有啲搵笨 同愛文有70%似 <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">雖然佢有愛文芒血統</span><br />\n德島奇異果 同 佐賀士多啤梨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbc94b0c89bc52022dcc56c545df62172b99f18a","tid":405172,"uid":16320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T17:49:39.000Z","msg":"岡山同香印有咩分別🤔<br />\n上次食左香印"},{"pid":"c84fe278c89060ea24dd0ab29821b82df22c613c","tid":405172,"uid":44559,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T18:01:55.000Z","msg":"我成日食，其實唔係真係好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而家食餐飯都要一舊，食生果可以接受la"},{"pid":"d553f9f010de483171115482b02182261c56da75","tid":405172,"uid":84367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T18:08:47.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"7755e0e7bb639683b9e2ba678a606169e3e9612e","tid":405172,"uid":106360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T18:15:28.000Z","msg":"好撚好食，唔識貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申窮撚 但有時都會買d晴王奬勵下自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"125c906a0baba3ffc66afd00569aeeb6ce648e98","tid":405172,"uid":14939,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T18:46:59.000Z","msg":"點解我覺得全部人係到吹緊水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3c5fb04a9d464bac8fd6d626a3bb5a0943dd3cb","tid":405172,"uid":55077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T18:51:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/361519/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/361519/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba08d793c1cfcda498f5380a90003eabad50cb9c","tid":405172,"uid":44233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T19:02:55.000Z","msg":"招換DDos巴打出黎屌醒啲唔識食嘅連登仔"},{"pid":"80feec6aa726f84a145d5387be9022ff6c336206","tid":405172,"uid":44233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T19:03:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>招換DDos巴打出黎屌醒啲唔識食嘅連登仔</blockquote><br />\n利申 日日食果欄生果 住係入面"},{"pid":"21817b89a3e10f6458c5f570962247b357b5e08a","tid":405172,"uid":14449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T19:03:51.000Z","msg":"連登好多有錢人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"649f62d7b382454dba66a8cd1982b34e9688fcbe","tid":405172,"uid":135381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T19:05:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>岡山同香印有咩分別🤔<br />\n上次食左香印</blockquote><br />\n你係唔係其實想問晴王同埋香印咩分別？晴王係岡山出產嘅香印，比其他產地嘅香印更加有香味。不過今年日本香印好差(日本農夫今年好急收割推出市場)，香味同往年差好遠。中國產嘅香印就好甜但係無香味(因為打針)。"},{"pid":"46a30c11e33676c3c15f10db217b8df5d91a0191","tid":405172,"uid":48834,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T19:10:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主試吓買個日本桃食，食完唔想食平時果啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  可以分享食評?</blockquote><br />\n又甜又多汁 食完唔撚明點解女人個閪會叫蜜桃"},{"pid":"b42a577e3adb5c35f3904d3597102b7c7636d071","tid":405172,"uid":126919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T19:33:09.000Z","msg":"住隔離，都係買普通嘢，日本生果好鬼貴，唔係成日買，主要係幫老母買玉林蘋果煲湯。"},{"pid":"c3006728b6d333af3db03479da55bf119e88e895","tid":405172,"uid":7796,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T19:40:44.000Z","msg":"樓主唔好咁井底啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" cla